com.b2international.snowowl.datastore.version

Class VersioningService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.datastore.version.VersioningService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IVersioningService
    Deprecated. 
    - use CodeSystemRequests.prepareNewCodeSystemVersion() instead

    public class VersioningService
extends java.lang.Object
implements IVersioningService
    Stateful versioning service implementation.

    Although this service is responsible for the whole versioning process it does not ensure locking on the underlying repositories.
    Clients are responsible to acquire lock in the desired repository.
